OL,7,F"I envisaged I would finish my working
OL,8,Fcareer in Irwin's bakery," Mr
OL,9,FGillespie told UTV.
OL,11,F"I love my job I loved what I was
OL,12,Fdoing I believed I was very good at it
OL,13,Fand I was so disappointed with the way
OL,14,Fit ended."
OL,16,FMr Gillespie, from Co Fermanagh,
OL,17,Fworked for the bakery since 1991.
