OL,8,F2021 that the company was looking for
OL,9,Fyounger professional people from a
OL,10,Fblue-chip background in the context of
OL,11,Frecruitment for new staff.
OL,13,FHe believes this was because the
OL,14,Fcompany thought the age profile of
OL,15,Fstaff within the business was a
OL,16,Fproblem.
