OL,7,FMr Gillespie also alleged that he was
OL,8,Finformed that he would lose some
OL,9,Faccounts when a vacant post of
OL,10,F'Business Unit Controller' was to be
OL,11,Ffilled.
OL,13,FHe believed that this resulted in him
OL,14,Flosing a significant proportion of his
OL,15,Fwork. He felt his role was diminished
OL,16,Fand that he was left in a vulnerable
OL,17,Fposition for possible future
OL,18,Fredundancy.
