OL,7,FIn August 2022, Mr Gillespie was
OL,8,Finformed of a project involving
OL,9,Fchanges in distribution. He believed
OL,10,Fthat he should have been included in
OL,11,Fthe relevant discussions because it
OL,12,Fimpacted upon his work.
OL,14,FMr Gillespie was advised in September
OL,15,F2022 that his post was at risk of
OL,16,Fredundancy. He was placed in a
OL,17,Fredundancy pool of one.
