OL,7,FDuring subsequent redundancy meetings,
OL,8,Fhe claims that comments were made
OL,9,Fregarding the need to get some new
OL,10,Fblood and of the age profile of the
OL,11,Fsenior management team being all of
OL,12,Fone ilk and age. Mr Gillespie was made
OL,13,Fredundant, and his appeal was not
OL,14,Fupheld.
OL,16,FMr Gillespie said: "I worked for
OL,17,FIrwins for over 30 years. I enjoyed my
OL,18,Fjob, I was a dedicated, hardworking
OL,19,Fand loyal employee, with lots of
OL,20,Fexperience.
