OL,7,F"But it was very clear to me,
OL,8,Ffollowing discussions with management,
OL,9,Fthat my career with the company was
OL,10,Fover.
OL,12,F"I firmly believed the decision to
OL,13,Fmake me redundant was based solely on
OL,14,Fmy age. I had no choice but to
OL,15,Fchallenge how I was treated. I'm glad
OL,16,Fmy case is now settled, although I
OL,17,Fwould rather that none of this had
OL,18,Fhappened in the first place."
