OL,7,FGeraldine McGahey, Chief Commissioner,
OL,8,FEquality Commission for Northern
OL,9,FIreland said: "Seamus gave 30 years of
OL,10,Fhis working life to Irwin's Bakery and
OL,11,Fstill had a lot to offer. He felt that
OL,12,Fhis age was a problem for his employer
OL,13,Fand believes that was why he was made
OL,14,Fredundant.
OL,16,F"In Northern Ireland it is unlawful to
OL,17,Fdiscriminate against employees because
OL,18,Fof their age.
