OL,7,F"Older workers have experience, skills
OL,8,Fand attributes that our economy needs
OL,9,Fto thrive, they are assets to their
OL,10,Femployers just like every other
OL,11,Femployee.
OL,13,F"It is imperative that employers have
OL,14,Frobust policies and practices in place
OL,15,Fto prevent any potential instances of
OL,16,Fage discrimination and that staff are
OL,17,Fadequately trained to use them,"
OL,18,Fconcluded Ms McGahey.
