OL,7,FA spokesperson for the bakery said:
OL,8,F"WD Irwin & Sons has always prided
OL,9,Fitself on its commitment to diversity
OL,10,Fin the workplace, and the company has
OL,11,Fsettled this case without admission of
OL,12,Fliability.
OL,14,F"The company has taken the opportunity
OL,15,Fto reaffirm its commitment to the
OL,16,Fprinciple of equality of opportunity
OL,17,Fand has liaised with the Commission to
OL,18,Fensure its policies, procedures,
OL,19,Fpractices, and existing training
OL,20,Fprogrammes continue to comply with the
OL,21,Flatest employment regulations."
